# ============================================
# ZERO-TH LAW: Project Absolute Isolation
# WHITE-LIST MODE: Only allow skill framework files
# ============================================

# ✅ ALLOW: Skill core files (explicitly whitelist)
!SKILL.md
!LICENSE
!skill.json
!package.json
!README-DEPLOY.md
!README.md
!USER_GUIDE.md
!USE_CASES.md
!COMPETITIVE_ADVANTAGE.md
!WEB_PUBLISH_GUIDE.md
!MULTI_PLATFORM_PUBLISH_GUIDE.md
